data.description: Elegant 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom Lakeview Home in Miami with Modern Amenities and Stunning Features! Nestled in the heart of Miami, Florida, with an impressive area of 3,989 SQFT, this property boasts copious space and indulges in luxury with its top-tier features and charming design. It has tastefully tiled floors and offers a wonderful pool area, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying family time, along with your private balcony overlooking Lake Galloway. The roof is two years old - Impact windows and doors.
